# 10/10 Upgrade — Implementation Plan

Fixing all issues from the review: hollow AI logic, WAV concat bug, zero tests, fragile parsing, silent errors, and missing edge case handling.

---

## Proposed Changes

### Core AI Engine

#### [MODIFY] [ai_engine.py](file:///d:/nutrabay/core/ai_engine.py)

**Problem:** Single truncate-and-pray GPT call with no retry, no post-processing, no quiz verification.

**Changes:**
1. **Smart SOP chunking** — replace `sop_text[:8000]` truncation with intelligent chunking that processes long SOPs in sections, then merges results
2. **Retry with exponential backoff** — wrap API call in retry logic (3 attempts) for transient failures
3. **Two-pass quiz verification** — after generating content, make a second GPT call specifically to verify each quiz answer is correct and fix any wrong ones
4. **Deeper validation** — validate quiz options format, step ordering, non-empty content fields
5. **Mark sample output clearly** — add `"is_sample": true` flag to hardcoded sample so UI can display a badge

---

### SOP Preprocessor (New)

#### [NEW] [sop_preprocessor.py](file:///d:/nutrabay/core/sop_preprocessor.py)

**Problem:** Raw text is dumped straight to GPT with `[Page X]` noise. No structure extraction.

**Changes:**
1. Strip `[Page X]` markers before AI processing  
2. Detect headings/sections using regex heuristics (ALL CAPS lines, numbered sections, lines ending with `:`)
3. Build a structured outline `{sections: [{heading, content}]}` before sending to GPT
4. Send the structured outline in the prompt so GPT has better context

